ZH: 我已经去过那个地方两次了。
EN: I have been to that place twice already.

ZH: 请再给我一次机会。
EN: Please give me another chance.

ZH: 我下次一定会记得带钱包。
EN: I will definitely remember to bring my wallet next time.

ZH: 他是我第一次见的人。
EN: He is someone I am meeting for the first time.

ZH: 这是我最后一次忍耐你的错误了。
EN: This is the last time I will tolerate your mistakes.

ZH: 我上次晚上熬夜，今天很困。
EN: I stayed up late last night, so I am very tired today.

ZH: 下次我们找一个更好的地方见面。
EN: Let's meet at a better place next time.

ZH: 我们还有多少次尝试的机会？
EN: How many more chances do we have to try?

ZH: 他的成绩这次比上次好多了。
EN: His grades are much better this time compared to last time.

ZH: 上次的聚会真的很有趣。
EN: The last party was really fun.

ZH: 下次开会的日期还没确定。
EN: The date for the next meeting is not yet determined.

ZH: 这次的挑战比上次难多了。
EN: This challenge is much harder than the last one.

ZH: 你觉得她下次还会来吗？
EN: Do you think she will come next time?

ZH: 这次旅行的总费用是多少？
EN: What is the total cost of this trip?

ZH: 你知道他下次来会待多久吗？
EN: Do you know how long he will stay next time?

ZH: 这次考试我们都没考好。
EN: None of us did well on this test.

ZH: 我下次见到她一定要向她道歉。
EN: I must apologize to her the next time I see her.

ZH: 你下次要来多久？
EN: How long will you stay next time?

ZH: 这次问题发生的原因是什么？
EN: What is the cause of this problem this time?

ZH: 他这次战胜了所有对手。
EN: He defeated all his opponents this time.

ZH: 我们明天有没有次会议？
EN: Do we have another meeting tomorrow?
